name: SolutionStatus
description: Represents the status of a solution.
summary: The object {SolutionStatus} for application {salesforce} represents the status of a solution in Salesforce. It has attributes such as Id, MasterLabel, ApiName, SortOrder, IsDefault, IsReviewed, CreatedById, CreatedDate, LastModifiedById, LastModifiedDate, and SystemModstamp. These attributes provide information about the status of a solution, including its labels, default status, review status, creation and modification details, and system timestamp.
label: Solution Status Value
